Part 9: The Review Questions
Daily Questions (2 minutes before bed)

Did I do something today that will grow WAR?
Did I activate or improve a product loop?
Did I ship something visible?

Weekly Questions (Monday morning)

What's my WAR this week vs. target?
Which loop needs most attention?
What's the highest-leverage activity I can do?

Monthly Questions (First Friday)

Are my loops getting stronger or weaker?
Is my velocity increasing or decreasing?
Am I building competitive moat or just doing sales?

Quarterly Questions (Strategic review)

Is 3% weekly realistic or should I adjust?
Which loop has highest ROI? Double down there.
What would Elena say about my distribution strategy?
What would YC say about my metric discipline?


